name: Compressed Pyroxeres III-Grade
description: III-Grade or viscous pyroxeres is the secret behind the success of ORE in the early days. ORE has since then moved into more profitable minerals, but viscous pyroxeres and its 10% higher mineral yield still holds a special place in the hearts of all miners dreaming of becoming the next mining moguls of EVE. Pyroxeres is a common ore available in all regions of space. It has fair amounts of Pyerite and Mexallon. This material is compressed and a much more compact form of the original material.
